<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 20:08:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列在约旦河西岸建立了25个新的非法哨所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-erected-25-new-illegal-outposts-in-west-bank-since-gaza-war-started/00000190-eb35-d298-a592-fb375f200000</link><description>非政府组织“立即和平”的一份新报告分析了以色列政府旨在深化吞并进程的各种行动，例如提前批准 8,721 个新住房单元并将约 9.3 平方英里划为国有土地</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-erected-25-new-illegal-outposts-in-west-bank-since-gaza-war-started/00000190-eb35-d298-a592-fb375f200000</guid></item><item><title>认识在巴黎争夺金牌的以色列奥运奖牌希望者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/meet-israels-olympic-medal-hopefuls-going-for-the-gold-in-paris/00000190-e9e2-d469-a39d-edf70d290000</link><description>艺术体操运动员 Artem Dolgopyat、艺术体操队、风帆冲浪运动员 Sharon Kantor 以及柔道运动员 Raz Hershko 和 Inbar Lanir 都是各自运动领域的佼佼者。但我们不要忘记黑马</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/meet-israels-olympic-medal-hopefuls-going-for-the-gold-in-paris/00000190-e9e2-d469-a39d-edf70d290000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷与巴比伦之间的航行：结束与开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/navigating-between-jerusalem-babylon-an-end-and-a-beginning/00000190-eabe-d45d-a5b3-ebbe6ec90000</link><description>现在不是结束《国土报》17年来关于犹太人身份的专栏的好时机——尤其是当人们如此不愿意谈论宗教在加沙战争中的作用时。但有一些东西我希望你能带走</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/navigating-between-jerusalem-babylon-an-end-and-a-beginning/00000190-eabe-d45d-a5b3-ebbe6ec90000</guid></item><item><title>人质家庭敦促以色列军队公布哈马斯在加沙扣押的亲属的照片和其他材料</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-pressing-idf-to-release-photos-other-material-of-kin-held-in-gaza/00000190-eb01-d32c-af96-fbe566ac0000</link><description>最近，一些家庭公开了从军队获得的照片和视频，以加大对政府签署人质协议的压力。军队已移交了家属要求的大部分材料，但仍持有数十张尚未要求的图片、视频和录音</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-pressing-idf-to-release-photos-other-material-of-kin-held-in-gaza/00000190-eb01-d32c-af96-fbe566ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，以色列士兵在加沙南部可能因吸入有毒气体而死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-due-to-possible-poisonous-gas-inhalation-idf-says/00000190-eb44-d298-a592-fb775a740000</link><description>参谋军士。军方称，诺姆·杜克于周四被杀，可能是吸入发电机中的有毒气体所致；另外两名士兵在同一事件中受重伤，被送往医院接受治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-due-to-possible-poisonous-gas-inhalation-idf-says/00000190-eb44-d298-a592-fb775a740000</guid></item><item><title>关于以色列发现的高致命病原体您需要了解的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-highly-lethal-pathogen-discovered-in-israel/00000190-eae2-d32c-af96-fbe6313c0000</link><description>什么是福氏耐格里阿米巴原虫，它是如何运作的以及是否可以保护自己免受感染？以色列北部最近发生病例后的综合指南</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 18:50:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-highly-lethal-pathogen-discovered-in-israel/00000190-eae2-d32c-af96-fbe6313c0000</guid></item><item><title>现在分散在以色列各地的独特的北方会众在战时还能保持在一起吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-a-unique-northern-congregation-scattered-across-israel-during-wartime-stay-together/00000190-e077-d9bf-a195-e5ff25500000</link><description>北部城市什莫纳 (Kiryat Shmona) 的进步犹太社区 Poteach Shearim 的成员被迫于 10 月逃离家园。 “一切都是挑战，”拉比奥里特·罗森布利特 (Rabbi Orit Rozenblit) 在过去几个月中说道，但她并不打算放弃她花了数年时间建设的社区</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 18:29:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-a-unique-northern-congregation-scattered-across-israel-during-wartime-stay-together/00000190-e077-d9bf-a195-e5ff25500000</guid></item><item><title>“是时候结束战争了”：内塔尼亚胡和拜登会面时，白宫表示人质协议比以往任何时候都更接近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-biden-at-white-house-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-eaec-d45d-a5b3-ebeed9260000</link><description>人质家属预计将出席白宫会议。除了释放人质的努力外，美国还寻求内塔尼亚胡关于停止战斗和加沙战后计划的最新信息。内塔尼亚胡周五还将在特朗普位于佛罗里达州的庄园会见特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 17:25:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-biden-at-white-house-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-eaec-d45d-a5b3-ebeed9260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 293 天：美国高级官员表示，停战谈判似乎已进入最后阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-293-truce-talks-appear-to-be-in-closing-stages-u-s-official-says/00000190-ead6-dd5f-af93-fbd686580000</link><description>据报道，美国、以色列和阿拉伯国家的官员支持任命前巴勒斯坦权力机构安全局长穆罕默德·达赫兰在战后管理加沙 ■ 英国预计将放弃对国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的要求的保留 ■ 澳大利亚因参与暴力而制裁七名以色列人在约旦河西岸针对巴勒斯坦人 ■ 战争进入 293 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 17:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-293-truce-talks-appear-to-be-in-closing-stages-u-s-official-says/00000190-ead6-dd5f-af93-fbd686580000</guid></item><item><title>与内塔尼亚胡会面前一天，特朗普表示以色列需要“快速”结束加沙战争，夺回人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/day-before-meeting-netanyahu-trump-says-israel-needs-to-end-war-fast-get-hostages-back/00000190-ea5f-d469-a39d-eedf17740000</link><description>这位前总统还批评了那些抗议以色列总理在美国国会演讲的人，呼吁以亵渎美国国旗的罪名判处一年监禁</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/day-before-meeting-netanyahu-trump-says-israel-needs-to-end-war-fast-get-hostages-back/00000190-ea5f-d469-a39d-eedf17740000</guid></item><item><title>利伯曼说，拒绝加入以色列军队的极端正统派应该获得犯罪记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/mk-lieberman-says-haredim-who-refuse-to-join-idf-should-get-criminal-record/00000190-ea52-dd5f-af93-fb52741b0000</link><description>以色列前国防部长阿维格多·利伯曼表示，“一名真正的正统派士兵——而不是冒充正统派的人——在以色列国防军服役是没有问题的。”他认为，极端正统派可以留在自己的社区内，同时接受世俗教育或征兵。到军队</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/mk-lieberman-says-haredim-who-refuse-to-join-idf-should-get-criminal-record/00000190-ea52-dd5f-af93-fb52741b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部警方延长对被控杀害 6 岁儿子的妇女的拘留期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/police-extend-detention-for-woman-accused-of-killing-6-year-old-son-in-central-israel/00000190-ea0a-d603-abb5-fb8b22d20000</link><description>上周，嫌疑人在一家商场袭击并打伤一名保安后被捕。几个小时后，她儿子的祖母在家里的公寓里发现了他的尸体，尸体上有暴力痕迹。邻居过去曾就她的行为向警方报告过</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/police-extend-detention-for-woman-accused-of-killing-6-year-old-son-in-central-israel/00000190-ea0a-d603-abb5-fb8b22d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在恐怖袭击中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-terror-ramming-attack/00000190-ea2b-d298-a592-fa3b3a0b0000</link><description>来自 Pardes Hannah-Karkur 的 24 岁阿里尔·托帕兹 (Ariel Topaz) 在 7 月初的恐怖袭击中受重伤，于周三死亡。他的母亲写道：“即使进行了所有的祈祷，不幸的是，下一个‘公告’是我的整个世界，我亲爱的儿子，我的爱丽儿”</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-dies-from-wounds-sustained-in-terror-ramming-attack/00000190-ea2b-d298-a592-fa3b3a0b0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和内塔尼亚胡的讲话展现出最鲜明和最黑暗的对比</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-and-netanyahus-speeches-showed-up-the-starkest-and-darkest-of-contrasts/00000190-e9c8-d541-adbc-f9f8fd9e0000</link><description>乔·拜登和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡之间在风格和实质上的差异在周三的演讲中最为明显。这是恩典与受害、真相与谎言、真实与虚假、真实与虚假的案例</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:28:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/biden-and-netanyahus-speeches-showed-up-the-starkest-and-darkest-of-contrasts/00000190-e9c8-d541-adbc-f9f8fd9e0000</guid></item><item><title>演讲内容有真实性吗？嗯，这确实是内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-25/ty-article-podcast/was-there-anything-authentic-about-the-speech-well-it-was-authentically-netanyahu/00000190-e9a7-d45d-a5b3-ebaf4c450000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:22:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-25/ty-article-podcast/was-there-anything-authentic-about-the-speech-well-it-was-authentically-netanyahu/00000190-e9a7-d45d-a5b3-ebaf4c450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队报告三名以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸高速公路枪击事件中受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-three-idf-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank-highway-shooting/00000190-e9a5-d298-a592-f9b7ebf60000</link><description>士兵们在绿线西岸城市盖勒吉利亚附近的 55 号高速公路上行驶时被枪杀。这些士兵的情况为中度和轻症，被疏散到卡法萨巴的梅尔医院。军方表示，目前正在寻找枪手</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-three-idf-soldiers-wounded-in-west-bank-highway-shooting/00000190-e9a5-d298-a592-f9b7ebf60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府敦促最高法院驳回巴勒斯坦权力机构针对恐怖受害者赔偿法的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-urges-top-court-to-reject-pa-petition-against-terror-victim-compensation-law/00000190-e95e-d8b8-a59a-edde2fd00000</link><description>7月初，巴勒斯坦权力机构首次向以色列法院提出请愿，要求他们驳回以色列议会允许恐怖袭击受害者起诉巴勒斯坦权力机构要求赔偿的法律。以色列政府要求法院驳回请愿书，称巴勒斯坦权力机构向恐怖分子及其家人支付报酬</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 12:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-urges-top-court-to-reject-pa-petition-against-terror-victim-compensation-law/00000190-e95e-d8b8-a59a-edde2fd00000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院声明：解释为何本格维尔部的非法枪支许可证尚未被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-to-state-explain-why-ben-gvirs-illegal-gun-licenses-havent-been-annulled/00000190-e8fe-d8b8-a59a-ecfe0aa10000</link><description>以色列高等法院正在审理一项请愿书，要求废除 12,000 多张枪支许可证，因为本-格维尔的部门显然没有遵循程序并非法发放枪支许可证</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-to-state-explain-why-ben-gvirs-illegal-gun-licenses-havent-been-annulled/00000190-e8fe-d8b8-a59a-ecfe0aa10000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔在联盟协议中控制了西岸非法建设执法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-gets-control-over-illegal-west-bank-construction-enforcement-in-coalition-deal/00000190-e8e1-d603-abb5-f9e3d36d0000</link><description>在正统派和本格维尔就另一项授权拉比理事会有权使用手机的法律达成协议后，以色列议会通过了这项将权力从斯莫特里奇转移到本格维尔的法律。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-gets-control-over-illegal-west-bank-construction-enforcement-in-coalition-deal/00000190-e8e1-d603-abb5-f9e3d36d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将于周四会见拜登和哈里斯，因为美国要求结束加沙战争的压力越来越大</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-will-meet-biden-harris-on-thursday-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-e921-d8b8-a59a-edbf12f00000</link><description>人质家属预计将出席白宫会议。除了释放人质的努力外，美国还向内塔尼亚胡寻求有关停止战斗和加沙战后计划的最新信息。内塔尼亚胡周五还将在特朗普位于佛罗里达州的庄园会见特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 09:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-will-meet-biden-harris-on-thursday-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-e921-d8b8-a59a-edbf12f00000</guid></item></channel></rss>